data.description: TRUE POCONO MOUNTAIN LIVING! This 5bd/2.5ba Colonial is nestled in the HEART of a STR FRIENDLY COMMUNITY, conveniently close to amenities, including an outdoor pool, basketball court, & playground. Also close to major highways & popular attractions. The SPACIOUS Living Room flows into the Kitchen, creating the perfect space for entertaining guests. The Kitchen has ample cabinet/counter space, while the adjacent Dining Room is perfect for hosting dinner parties. A unique feature of this home is the SPA ROOM, complete w/ a relaxing hot tub. A bd & half bth are also on this floor. Upstairs, you'll find 4 SPACIOUS bds, including the Primary Suite w/ a walk-in closet & ensuite. This home also has a deck to take in the beauty of the Poconos & is on a peaceful corner lot! Homes like this don't come along often in this price range. Don't miss the chance to make this rare find your own!
